{"tha-ap113:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap113:0.2":"Mahaparivaravagga ","tha-ap113:0.3":"1 Mahaparivarakattheraapadana ","tha-ap113:1.1":"“Vipassi nama bhagava, ","tha-ap113:1.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap113:1.3":"Atthasatthisahassehi, ","tha-ap113:1.4":"pavisi bandhumam tada. ","tha-ap113:2.1":"Nagara abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap113:2.2":"agamam dipacetiyam; ","tha-ap113:2.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap113:2.4":"ahutinam patiggaham. ","tha-ap113:3.1":"Cullasitisahassani, ","tha-ap113:3.2":"yakkha mayham upantike; ","tha-ap113:3.3":"Upatthahanti sakkaccam, ","tha-ap113:3.4":"indamva tidasa gana. ","tha-ap113:4.1":"Bhavana abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap113:4.2":"dussam paggayhaham tada; ","tha-ap113:4.3":"Sirasa abhivadesim, ","tha-ap113:4.4":"tancadasim mahesino. ","tha-ap113:5.1":"Aho buddha aho dhamma, ","tha-ap113:5.2":"aho no satthu sampada; ","tha-ap113:5.3":"Buddhassa anubhavena, ","tha-ap113:5.4":"vasudhayam pakampatha. ","tha-ap113:6.1":"Tanca acchariyam disva, ","tha-ap113:6.2":"abbhutam lomahamsanam; ","tha-ap113:6.3":"Buddhe cittam pasademi, ","tha-ap113:6.4":"dvipadindamhi tadine. ","tha-ap113:7.1":"Soham cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap113:7.2":"dussam datvana satthuno; ","tha-ap113:7.3":"Sarananca upagacchim, ","tha-ap113:7.4":"samacco saparijjano. ","tha-ap113:8.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap113:8.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap113:8.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap113:8.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap113:9.1":"Ito pannarase kappe, ","tha-ap113:9.2":"solasasum suvahana; ","tha-ap113:9.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap113:9.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap113:10.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap113:10.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap113:10.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap113:10.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap113:11.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mahaparivarako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap113:12.1":"Mahaparivarakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}